  <h2>🌐 About the Website</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Vaultera is a smart, modern college Management System (CMS) designed for colleges to digitally streamline their operations.</li>
    <li>It offers secure role-based dashboards for HODs, Teachers, and Students, with the ability to manage and access academic files and assignments easily.</li>
    <li>Using technologies like AI, users can summarize documents, extract topic-based insights, and view important questions — all in a click.</li>
    <li>The platform aims to reduce manual paperwork, improve accessibility, and bring smarter collaboration between faculty and students.</li>
    <li>Features include file uploads, student/teacher onboarding, assignment submissions, and AI-enhanced tools for better academic performance.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>🤖 Smart AI Assistance</h2>
